      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted (coarse: 4.2M, medium: 11.7M, fine: 28.4M cells). GCI for wall shear stress is 1.8% and for velocity magnitude is 1.2%, both below the 3% threshold. Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence. Achieved level exceeds required level for MRL 2."
