      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index is the accepted regulatory endpoint for CPB device hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance. Wall shear stress and scalar stress are mechanistically linked to red blood cell damage. QoIs are directly relevant to the COU decision criterion."
