      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence demonstrated via residual monitoring; solution independence from initial conditions verified for at least one operating point.",
      "rationale": "Residuals for continuity, momentum, and turbulence quantities converge to below 1e-5 for all operating points. Mass imbalance is below 0.01%. Independence from two distinct initial conditions verified at the 4 L/min, 2500 RPM operating point. Achieved level exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
