      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal uncertainty quantification of model inputs is not required. Nominal values for all inputs (geometry dimensions, fluid viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients) are documented with literature or measurement sources. Sensitivity to key inputs (viscosity ±10%) was informally assessed and found to have negligible effect on RH predictions."
